quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  18,13,"Menen Me…óen fillanaade ma kumpital fii ma…ď…ďe e Goonga, …ďen …óon, ko sukaa…ďe gom…óin…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe Men …ďeydani …ďe Peewal"
  18,14,"Men ha…ď…ďi e dow …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe tuma nde …ďe darinoo, …ďe wi'i: \"Joomi amen ko Jey…óo On kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, men noddataa ko woori Mo rewetee…óo, gom…óii haray men wi'ii ontuma [konngol] fantungol"
  18,15,"∆Āee yim…ďe amen, …ďe jogitike ko woori Mo rewetee…ói, ko haaanunoo ko yo …ďe addu e dow ma…ď…ďe dalil …ďanngu…óo. Ko hommbo …ďuri too√Īude ko foti e on fefindii…óo fenaande o fawi e Alla"
  18,16,"Tuma nde wo…ó…óitino…óon …ďe e ko …ďe rewata kon ko woori Alla, …ďe soroyi ka fammeere Joomi mon fontani on e Yurmeende Makko nden O newinani on e fiyaake mon neweende"
  18,17,"Hi…óa yi'a naangi ngen si nge ∆īellitike hinge naayora ka fammeere ma…ď…ďe senngo √Īaamo, si hinge mutude nge mutiranay …ďe ka senngo nano, kam…ďe hi…ďe e yaajeende e …óun, …óun ko jeyaa…óun e Aayeeje Alla, on mo Alla fewni ko on woni feewu…óo, kala moO majjini a he…ďantaa mo hettu…óo fewnoowo. @Corrected"